This paper is primarily focused on the problem of vulnerability detection in software programs, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques for this purpose, which involves the application of machine learning algorithms to large datasets, and thus could also be classified under the categories of software engineering (cs.SE), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and programming languages (cs.PL).
